name: NAV
public_notice: According to GoPlus, the contract creator can make changes to the token contract such as disabling sells, changing fees, minting, transferring tokens etc. Exercise caution.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: NAV Finance is a regulated on-chain hedge fund that provides Structured Investment Products (SIPs) tailored for high-growth opportunities in DeFi. NAV combines institutional-grade portfolio management with on-chain transparency, allowing investors to access narrative-driven strategies, cross-chain yield maximization, and innovative staking models. The fund actively manages risk through dynamic asset allocation, liquid staking, and leveraged yield strategies, ensuring optimized performance in both bullish and bearish market conditions.
